									</div>
			
			<div class="feature-content">
				<h2 class="node-title">
					<a href="          https://www.livingwage.org.uk/what-real-living-wage    
">What is the Living Wage?</a>
				</h2>
				<div class="field field-name-field-long-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>The real Living Wage is based on the cost of living and is voluntarily paid by 3,500 UK employers who believe a fair day's work deserves a fair day's pay.</p></div></div></div>									<a class="read-more" href="          https://www.livingwage.org.uk/what-real-living-wage    
">Read more</a>
					
			</div>
		  
  <div class="clearfix">
          <nav class="links node-links clearfix"></nav>
    
      </div>
</article></div><div class="field-item odd"><article about="/why-pay-real-living-wage" typeof="sioc:Item foaf:Document" class="node node-media-text-feature node-promoted node-published node-not-sticky author-katy-jockelson odd clearfix" id="node-media-text-feature-5509">
        <header></header>
    <span property="dc:title" content="Why Pay the real Living Wage?" class="rdf-meta element-hidden"></span>    
  
  <div class="content clearfix">
    	  	  	  	
