									</div>
			
			<div class="feature-content">
				<h2 class="node-title">
					<a href="          https://www.livingwage.org.uk/good-for-business    
">Why Pay the real Living Wage?</a>
				</h2>
				<div class="field field-name-field-long-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>As well as being good for society, there are significant business benefits to paying the real Living Wage.</p></div></div></div>									<a class="read-more" href="          https://www.livingwage.org.uk/good-for-business    
">Read more</a>
					
			</div>
		  
