			<div class="feature-content">
				<h2 class="node-title">
					<a href="          https://www.livingwage.org.uk/accredited-living-wage-employers    
">Who pays the Living Wage?</a>
				</h2>
				<div class="field field-name-field-long-text field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>There are 3,800 Living Wage employers, including 1/3 of the FTSE 100 and household names including Ikea, Aviva, Nationwide and Everton FC.</p>

<p> </p></div></div></div>									<a class="read-more" href="          https://www.livingwage.org.uk/accredited-living-wage-employers    
